{"tid":1364124,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"星期六元朗推演 遊行無差佬>黑社會開拖>狗兩邊都拉人拎光環","createTime":"2019-07-25T09:44:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-25T11:22:00.000Z","uid":15644,"like":67,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"b1b99610b33826ac562b3a8a4e69a5536516be56","tid":1364124,"uid":15644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T09:44:02.000Z","msg":"狗:無預計有大量人群於元朗聚集<br />\n收到報案已立即出動<br />\n成功拘捕大量毆鬥人士<br />\n完美維穩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔好講話乜野去遊行無諗住打<br />\n黑社會打到埋黎<br />\n到時一定會打番轉頭<br />\n打成點贏唔贏到就唔知<br />\n但係個結果就一定係上面咁<br />\n唔會有第二個<br />\n<br />\n你話人多就一定無事其實都係好閪蠢既諗法<br />\n因為每次出事都係已經天黑大部分人走左<br />\n剩低一部份勇武+ 想保護勇武既人<br />\n<br />\n一d 話走一d 話唔好走<br />\n唔知走唔去亂撚唒<br />\n然後比人圍毆<br />\n次次都係咁<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果唔解決上述問題<br />\n星期六必敗"},{"pid":"b8b9e861e793046be361895fd30bdfe97cd024a2","tid":1364124,"uid":278783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T09:44:57.000Z","msg":"王道劇本"},{"pid":"0d49f7455185beaf3ecd844e7a30634256df6625","tid":1364124,"uid":24443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T09:45:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eebcb5d2732f0b3dd4e134eeab330f3c858cd84a","tid":1364124,"uid":15644,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"0d49f7455185beaf3ecd844e7a30634256df6625","tid":1364124,"uid":24443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T09:45:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T09:50:13.000Z","msg":"公子獻頭呢鋪"},{"pid":"e99106a67ab14a92ae50666c572bcd06322a3e24","tid":1364124,"uid":8600,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T09:54:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cca44f27e27bff4530beae2a3e46aefedc2c5546","tid":1364124,"uid":126730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sc